237
00:16:31,541 --> 00:16:35,981
<font color=#FFFF00>Bom selalu sendirian
sebelum bertemu Shi Kyung.</font>

238
00:16:36,970 --> 00:16:40,653
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tampak begitu kuat,
