248
00:17:37,050 --> 00:17:38,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

249
00:17:58,163 --> 00:17:59,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini.</font>

250
00:18:07,017 --> 00:18:09,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana? Enak, 'kan?</font>

