289
00:20:24,601 --> 00:20:25,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Suk Joo Yeon.</font>

290
00:20:26,988 --> 00:20:28,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita bicara.</font>

291
00:20:32,958 --> 00:20:35,315
