536
00:43:14,719 --> 00:43:16,451
<font color=#FFFF00>Bernard selalu melihat ke arah ini.</font>

537
00:43:19,237 --> 00:43:20,677
<font color=#FFFF00>Bong Gu, kau membersihkannya dengan baik.</font>

538
00:43:31,807 --> 00:43:32,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini...</font>

539
00:43:33,556 --> 00:43:37,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan lagi kita bisa bertukar
