626
00:51:21,669 --> 00:51:23,451
<font color=#FFFF00>Bom pergi ke Seoul besok.</font>

627
00:51:25,044 --> 00:51:26,363
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibunya menjemputnya.</font>

628
00:51:27,515 --> 00:51:31,373
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, haruskah
